Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.20,0:18:31.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,0)\shad1\fs22\bord1.5\an8\u1}Board:\N{\u0}Zange-chan Original CD Debut!!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.63,0:13:56.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)\shad1\fs22\bord1.5\an8\u1}TL-Note:\N{\u0}In Buddhism, 49 days is the time it takes for a soul to reborn again into a new life.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.03,0:00:07.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, darling.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.91,0:00:10.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The girl that ran away from home, how long is she going to stay here?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.97,0:00:13.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's wait and see for the time being.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.87,0:00:16.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She said she's Obaa-chan's friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.01,0:00:27.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How are you feeling? Are you able to go home?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.55,0:00:28.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shall I help you make a call?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.45,0:00:36.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your family must be worried about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.80,0:00:43.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm ashamed...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.92,0:00:46.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.06,0:00:49.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've been walking a tightrope all this while.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.98,0:00:51.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.22,0:00:59.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've always taken for granted that he'll take care of me... {tlc. who take care of who?} {est: I can't tell him it's for gratned that he has to take care of me...}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.44,0:01:01.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't say that...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.29,0:01:04.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can think about it after you've calmed down.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.07,0:01:05.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go to the living room.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.45,0:01:08.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We have cake. Shall I pour some tea for you?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.01,0:01:13.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She left?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.55,0:01:15.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.55,0:01:19.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey... Have you gone to look for her?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.37,0:01:22.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't find her.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.75,0:01:24.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh? You couldn't?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.99,0:01:26.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Have you gone to the police?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.83,0:01:29.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just forget about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.11,0:01:30.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean, forget about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.28,0:01:32.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jin!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.51,0:01:40.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's none of your business.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.54,0:02:28.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, whatever happened to Nagi-sama?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.14,0:02:29.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You mean...?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.79,0:02:32.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like she's absent again today.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.26,0:02:35.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yesterday, Mikuriya was acting strange too.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.20,0:02:37.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know what happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.83,0:02:40.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think it's better if you ask Jin directly...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.04,0:02:45.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even {\i1}I{\i0}  know how to read the atmosphere. That's why I'm asking you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.41,0:02:47.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're Mikuriya's guardian, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.42,0:02:49.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Guardian? That's not...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.13,0:02:53.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't really know...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.08,0:02:57.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think you need to worry so much, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.41,0:03:00.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look, Nagi-san might be throwing a tantrum, just like last time.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.97,0:03:02.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Last time?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.55,0:03:04.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you mean the closet incident?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.59,0:03:07.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure something like that must have happened again.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.79,0:03:10.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She'll be back in no time.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.89,0:03:12.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You think so?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.03,0:03:17.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it's concerning the two of them, so I don't think we need to butt in.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.52,0:03:21.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see, they're siblings after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.54,0:03:24.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is where we shouldn't be stepping in, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.71,0:03:30.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Is love a calamity?", I asked out of the blue.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.13,0:03:37.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"A calamity, indeed.", replied the teacher in the same serious tone.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.27,0:03:42.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Why? I will know why in time to come."
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.05,0:03:46.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"No, you already knew."
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.34,0:03:53.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Hasn't your heart been in motion because of love, ever since ages ago?"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.13,0:03:57.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I tried searching my heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.89,0:04:01.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But it was emptier than I expected.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.38,0:04:02.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, that'll be enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.62,0:04:09.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At this point, Nou-sensei unexpectedly showed strong emotions in response to my questions.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.59,0:04:14.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This can be forgiven in view of Sensei's past, which will be described later.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.21,0:04:17.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This has nothing to do with you, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.59,0:04:22.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mikuriya!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.64,0:04:24.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.45,0:04:26.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you hungry or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.40,0:04:28.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.20,0:04:42.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't push yourself too hard, Mikuriya.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.14,0:05:02.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't the time to be spacing out. You have to look for Nagi-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.85,0:05:04.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I did.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.66,0:05:09.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, what did you do to Nagi-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.48,0:05:13.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A little squabble.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.40,0:05:14.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's all?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.58,0:05:21.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She left on her own volition.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.33,0:05:24.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have no right to stop her at this point in time.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.92,0:05:29.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She doesn't have any reason to stay in my house too.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.80,0:05:34.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If she can't stand being around any longer, she'll just need to go somewhere else.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.33,0:05:39.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? What nonsense are you saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.59,0:05:44.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't it obvious that she can't come back because she doesn't want to give in to you? {tlc}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.74,0:05:47.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She has nowhere else to go besides your house!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.66,0:05:51.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She said you're her family.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.10,0:05:53.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Normally, nobody would say such a thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.21,0:05:56.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What she meant was that you're important to her! She wants you to go after her!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.44,0:05:58.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She must be wanting to go home now! {tlc}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.00,0:06:03.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, I've thought too highly of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.69,0:06:06.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So this is how little she meant to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.92,0:06:08.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you think you're too unfeeling?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.02,0:06:12.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You actually want her to come back, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.26,0:06:15.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But you don't dare to face her, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.06,0:06:16.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why you're only running away, aren't you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.24,0:06:18.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nagi-san said this before.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.72,0:06:21.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"When in doubt, act according to your intuition and emotion."
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.82,0:06:25.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gosh, why's this child so oblivious to his own feelings?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.01,0:06:31.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jin.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.76,0:06:33.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.72,0:06:53.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jin? Everyone has posted that they've seen her.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.37,0:06:57.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems that she's walking around town now.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.97,0:07:00.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really? Why does everyone...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.77,0:07:04.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nagi-san's famous around here, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.76,0:07:07.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Information will come flying in whenever she goes out.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.32,0:07:11.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't check because you don't have a computer at home, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.45,0:07:12.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Be grateful! {Tsugumi is the ultimate osananajimi ;_;}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.52,0:07:15.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Tsugumi!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.01,0:07:20.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen up. The newest info we have now is...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.69,0:07:31.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She claims to be a god, yet nothing is known about her...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.28,0:07:36.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a wonder how you could've lived with something like that for so long.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.82,0:07:38.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's because...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.63,0:07:41.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's because it's been fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.47,0:07:44.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyday was fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.34,0:08:05.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nagi!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.51,0:08:23.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nagi...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.30,0:08:42.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean, you were lying to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.50,0:08:48.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You didn't mean to lie, am I right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.76,0:08:52.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't even understand yourself, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.63,0:08:55.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't know about the impurities, or why you have memory lapses!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.97,0:09:00.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't know anything, and you tried to keep it from me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.68,0:09:02.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because you don't know anything and you're afraid.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.80,0:09:09.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But who cares about all those?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.43,0:09:12.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I believe that you're a god!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.94,0:09:16.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if you can't remember, I've met you before when I was a child!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.22,0:09:20.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've come so far because I hold those memories close to my heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.78,0:09:32.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I... I think I'm a god.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.20,0:09:36.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think I am...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.58,0:09:41.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I can't substantiate it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.67,0:09:45.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My sense of self that's supporting me is lacking!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.30,0:09:53.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ambiguous? Inadequate?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.87,0:09:55.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.11,0:09:59.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is this... fragile sense of self?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.76,0:10:05.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yet I had the cheek to maintain my pride for so long...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.36,0:10:08.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why we should look for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.71,0:10:14.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be seeing you even if you go into memory lapses.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.37,0:10:16.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Together, we can find the answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.48,0:10:18.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's look for it together, Nagi!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.36,0:10:20.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's find the true cause of your uneasiness!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.33,0:10:57.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.44,0:10:59.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wipe your nose.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.88,0:11:10.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm ashamed...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.18,0:11:13.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank goodness.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.56,0:11:16.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see that you found your family.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.03,0:11:18.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shige.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.65,0:11:21.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh my!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.67,0:11:22.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.29,0:11:25.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What strange fate!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.50,0:11:29.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can tell you more if you wish. How about it? {Oh hay, a MILF!}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.44,0:11:43.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That road was where the portable Shinto shrine passed through.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.42,0:11:46.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's around the place where the apartments were built. {mansion in jap = apartment in eng, right?}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.89,0:11:48.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you remember, Kannagi-sama?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.14,0:11:53.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On both sides were our field.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.31,0:11:57.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,During spring, the field of rape blossoms was a sight to behold.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.24,0:12:01.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I... remember...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.99,0:12:06.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next to it was a field of Chinese milk vetches. {rengesou - chinese milk vetch???} {est: yeah it's not lotus}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.19,0:12:16.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those were hard times.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.02,0:12:20.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My husband went to war; my children and I were left behind.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.40,0:12:23.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that's right. It was I who hung myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.35,0:12:29.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard that my husband died in battle in the southern countries.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.13,0:12:33.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That made me lose myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.39,0:12:35.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I already had children, and yet...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.12,0:12:42.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Back then, there were many people like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.28,0:12:48.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But the land deity here could not allow anyone to throw their lives away.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.34,0:12:54.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I tied a rope to that tree, but the branch broke.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.48,0:12:57.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even though its thickness was such that it shouldn't have.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.80,0:13:05.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've always believed that you were watching over me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.64,0:13:09.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was really happy that you came for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.65,0:13:16.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was relieved.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.24,0:13:26.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That has to be the second time I saw you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.57,0:13:31.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The first time was when I was born.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.22,0:13:36.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You are the chime that signals life, and death.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.72,0:13:42.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've always had the feeling that I can meet you at the entrance and exit of the stage of life. {tlc} {est: orz}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.63,0:13:52.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I plan to take things at my own pace for these 49 days.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.08,0:13:56.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See you again on the day of departure, Kannagi-sama. {est, what's day of departure?} {est: im not buddhist but i think after 49 days the spirit departs, thus the spirit goes away from this god's land possibly to another land}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.89,0:14:12.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nagi, that woman...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.55,0:14:18.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The first family of my followers.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.15,0:14:22.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The god-protector, the family of Kamimori.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.34,0:14:32.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was hard to understand... {tlc} {est: That was hard to figure out (orz)}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.42,0:14:35.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You didn't understand, huh? {tlc} {est: You didn't understand it?}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.21,0:14:38.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jin.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.85,0:14:43.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it all right for me to call myself a god?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.60,0:14:48.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shige said those things to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.12,0:14:51.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My memories are murky.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.76,0:14:58.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Most likely, I appeared before her when I lost my consciousness...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.22,0:15:03.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Such an ambiguous sense of self... I...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.28,0:15:07.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everything will be fine, Nagi!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.48,0:15:12.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't you say just now that you remembered what happened in the past?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.60,0:15:16.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even I don't know much about myself yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.32,0:15:21.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I think we just have to search and ponder.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.14,0:15:23.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure we'll find some hints.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.78,0:15:24.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's rack our brains together.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.38,0:15:28.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.29,0:15:50.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm back.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.36,0:16:06.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Replaying messages.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.75,0:16:09.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mikuriya! I saw the message board!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.99,0:16:12.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So what on earth happened between you and Nagi-sama?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.46,0:16:14.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'd better tell me tomorrow!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.36,0:16:16.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shino, say something too!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.34,0:16:20.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't go too far with your fights and make-ups.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.20,0:16:22.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bye, Nagi-sama! See you tomorrow!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.55,0:16:27.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello, it's me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.16,0:16:30.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll bring the videos tomorrow. Tell Nagi-san for me, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.91,0:16:36.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll call again.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.97,0:16:41.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll call again.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.91,0:16:48.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why's my timing...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.01,0:16:51.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I can just tell you in person tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.28,0:16:53.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, tell Nagi-san-
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.89,0:17:04.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone was worried about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.69,0:17:08.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll apologize tomorrow at school.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.95,0:17:11.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yup. At school.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.72,0:17:21.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jin, I'm going to take a bath.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.71,0:17:22.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.88,0:17:29.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Umm... Jin.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.76,0:17:32.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.07,0:17:34.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.03,0:17:53.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.76,0:18:12.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In commemoration of my CD release,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.40,0:18:15.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll hold a handshake meeting and a confession meeting.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.63,0:18:17.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well then!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.05,0:18:21.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In commemoration of the release, I'll sing a bit of the new song!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.18,0:18:26.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnArial} ♪ {\r}My feelings for you are crescendo{est: music language}{\fnArial} ♪{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.24,0:18:29.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnArial} ♪ {\r}ride upon the dolphins{\fnArial} ♪ {\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.64,0:18:30.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnArial} ♪ {\r}and reach you{\fnArial} ♪ {\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.22,0:18:33.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnArial} ♪ {\r}Yes we can~{\fnArial} ♪ {\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.56,0:18:36.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnArial} ♪ {\r}Sometimes I lost my way{\fnArial} ♪ {\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.33,0:18:38.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnArial} ♪ {\r}And might look at other people-{\fnArial} ♪ {\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.97,0:19:13.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnArial} ♪ {\r}Even if you become a beast{\fnArial} ♪ {\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.67,0:19:18.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnArial} ♪ {\r}God will definitely forgive you-{\fnArial} ♪ {\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.25,0:18:54.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I forgot to bring a second set of clothes!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.24,0:18:57.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to get my acts together!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.66,0:19:10.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can I just run and take my clothes?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.97,0:19:26.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cool down, cool down!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.25,0:19:30.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If this goes on, I can't look at Nagi in the face.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.37,0:19:35.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.43,0:19:38.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Watch out!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.10,0:19:47.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ji... Jin.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.99,0:19:54.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Na... Nagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.58,0:19:57.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.69,0:19:59.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.47,0:20:01.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I...!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.33,0:20:04.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jin? I heard that Nagi-san's back!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.39,0:20:05.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You should've called me...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.61,0:20:21.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.99,0:20:26.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Wait, Tsugumi!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.31,0:20:27.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can explain this!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.26,0:20:28.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get off of me now!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.39,0:20:30.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What explanation? Perverted Jin!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.10,0:20:30.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Perverted human!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.80,0:20:34.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.12,0:20:36.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why am I crying?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.62,0:20:39.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing, getting a free glimpse of me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.22,0:20:44.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't see anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.68,0:20:47.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not the crucial parts.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.01,0:20:53.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Say, he'll surely make fun of me if he saw these.
